# Backend — {{ project_name }}

Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin 2.2+, Java 21) backend service.

## Quick Reference

- **Build**: `./gradlew build` (or `gradlew.bat build` on Windows)
- **Run**: `./gradlew bootRun`
- **Test**: `./gradlew test`
- **Port**: 8080 (configurable via `PORT` env var)

## Architecture

```
src/main/kotlin/{{ package_identifier | replace('.', '/') }}/
  bootstrap/         → Framework config (Security, CORS, OAuth2, OpenAPI)
    security/        → JWT token provider and authentication filter
  shared/            → Cross-cutting concerns (exceptions, models, audit)
    audit/           → AuditableEntity base class (createdAt/updatedAt)
    exception/       → ApiException hierarchy + GlobalExceptionHandler
    model/           → Shared DTOs (ApiErrorResponse, PagedResponse)
  modules/           → Feature modules
    auth/            → Authentication (OAuth + {% if "password" in auth_methods %}password + {% endif %}JWT)
      controller/    → REST endpoints
      dto/           → Request/response data classes
      model/         → User entity + enums
      repository/    → JPA repository
      service/       → Auth + OAuth2 business logic
    example/         → Example CRUD feature (template for new features)
      controller/    → REST endpoints
      dto/           → Request/response data classes
      model/         → Example entity + enums
      repository/    → JPA repository
      service/       → Business logic + permission checks
```

## Conventions

- **Package per feature**: each feature in `modules/{name}/` with controller, dto, model, repository, service subpackages
- **DTOs in `dto/`**: separate from entities in `model/` — never expose entities directly
- **Entities extend `AuditableEntity`**: provides `createdAt`/`updatedAt` via `@MappedSuperclass`
- **Exceptions**: throw `ApiException` subclasses — `GlobalExceptionHandler` maps to JSON
- **Auth**: JWT Bearer token; `@AuthenticationPrincipal user: User` in controllers
- **Migrations**: Flyway in `resources/db/migration/V{N}__{description}.sql`
- **Tests**: `@SpringBootTest` + `@ActiveProfiles("test")` with H2 in-memory DB

## Key Files

- `bootstrap/SecurityConfig.kt` — endpoint security rules, JWT filter
- `bootstrap/OAuth2Config.kt` — OAuth provider credentials
- `bootstrap/security/JwtTokenProvider.kt` — token generation/validation
- `shared/audit/AuditableEntity.kt` — base entity with timestamps
- `application.yml` — all configuration (DB, JWT, OAuth, CORS)
- `resources/db/migration/V1__init.sql` — initial schema

